OL,3,CBuilding work begins on memorial for
OL,4,Cfamilies affected by Legacy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FBuilding work has begun on a memorial
OL,8,Fgarden to remember those affected by
OL,9,Fthe Legacy funeral directors
OL,10,Finvestigation have been confirmed.
OL,12,FThe site at Northern Cemetary will
OL,13,Finclude name plaques, seating, and
OL,14,Fbird baths and is set to be completed
OL,15,Fby late September.
OL,17,FA private ceremony for families and
OL,18,Floved ones to inter ashes at the
OL,19,FNorthern Cemetery memorial will take
OL,20,Fplace later this summer.
