OL,3,CBuilding work begins on memorial for
OL,4,Cfamilies affected by Legacy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt is one of two memorial gardens
OL,8,Fplanned following a consultation
OL,9,Fearlier this year by Hull City Council
OL,10,Fand East Riding of Yorkshire Council.
OL,12,FWork is expected to begin later this
OL,13,Fmonth at the second site at Lelley
OL,14,FFields Crematorium near Preston.
OL,16,FIt came after an investigation into
OL,17,Fthe treatment of bodies at a funeral
OL,18,Fdirectors in Hull.
