OL,7,FHull City Council's director of adult
OL,8,Fsocial care, Tracy Meyerhoff, said
OL,9,Fminor changes have been made following
OL,10,Finput from families.
OL,12,F"Whilst the overall look of the
OL,13,Fgardens will remain largely the same,
OL,14,Fthat feedback has led to some minor
OL,15,Fchanges.
