OL,7,F"We're happy to make these suggested
OL,8,Fadditions so that we can make sure
OL,9,Fthat the gardens will be respectful
OL,10,Fand peaceful settings where ashes of
OL,11,Fthose involved can be laid to rest,
OL,12,Fincluding the interment of ashes at
OL,13,Fthe Hull site."
OL,15,FIn March last year, Humberside Police
OL,16,Fsaid they removed 35 bodies and a
OL,17,Fquantity of ashes from Legacy after
OL,18,Freceiving a report of concern for care
OL,19,Ffor the deceased in March last year.
