OL,4,Cfamilies affected by Legacy
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FRobert Bush, the owner of Hull's
OL,8,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors,
OL,9,Fwas charged with 30 counts of
OL,10,Fpreventing a lawful and decent burial
OL,11,Fand 30 counts of fraud by false
OL,12,Frepresentation relating to bodies
OL,13,Ffound at the firm's Hessle Road site
OL,14,Fin Hull in March last year.
OL,16,FThe independent charity Victim Support
OL,17,Fcontinues to run a dedicated helpline
OL,18,Fand support service for anyone
OL,19,Faffected by the incident on 0808 281
OL,20,F1136, or visit the Victim Support
OL,21,FLegacy webpage.
